00:35:08.920 --> 00:35:09.420
All right.

00:35:09.420 --> 00:35:11.280
Over here?

00:35:11.280 --> 00:35:13.530
AUDIENCE: It's an honor to
be here with you, Dr. Kaku.

00:35:13.530 --> 00:35:15.990
I have a question, a simple one.

00:35:15.990 --> 00:35:20.673
Do you believe humans will
reach a Type 1 civilization?

00:35:20.673 --> 00:35:21.340
MICHIO KAKU: OK.

00:35:21.340 --> 00:35:23.660
A type-- I'm a physicist.

00:35:23.660 --> 00:35:29.630
We rank civilizations by two
things, energy and information.

00:35:29.630 --> 00:35:34.720
That's how we rank anything,
energy, information.

00:35:34.720 --> 00:35:38.620
Energy of a planet
eventually reaches Type 1.

00:35:38.620 --> 00:35:42.940
So that Earth becomes
planetary, we, for example,

00:35:42.940 --> 00:35:44.980
can control the weather.

00:35:44.980 --> 00:35:46.750
We can mine the oceans.

00:35:46.750 --> 00:35:50.080
Type 2 is stellar,
where you then

00:35:50.080 --> 00:35:55.030
begin to consume the power
of a star, like "Star Trek."

00:35:55.030 --> 00:35:58.210
"Star Trek" would be
a Type 2 civilization

00:35:58.210 --> 00:36:00.490
where they've colonized
a few solar systems,

00:36:00.490 --> 00:36:01.660
but not much more.

00:36:01.660 --> 00:36:08.200
Type 3 is galactic, a galactic
civilization like "Star Wars",

00:36:08.200 --> 00:36:10.960
where you can roam the
galactic space lane.

00:36:10.960 --> 00:36:12.490
Now what are we?

00:36:12.490 --> 00:36:16.540
Are we Type 1 that can mine the
ocean, play with the weather?

00:36:16.540 --> 00:36:19.230
Are we Type 2 that
play with stars?

00:36:19.230 --> 00:36:22.180
Are we Type 3 that
play with black holes?

00:36:22.180 --> 00:36:25.680
No, we're Type 0.

00:36:25.680 --> 00:36:28.050
We don't even rate
on this scale.

00:36:28.050 --> 00:36:32.410
We get our energy from
dead plants, oil and coal.

00:36:32.410 --> 00:36:36.900
So we have all the savagery
of a Type 0 civilization--

00:36:36.900 --> 00:36:40.170
sectarianism, religious
hatred, racism,

00:36:40.170 --> 00:36:42.660
all the garbage from the past.

00:36:42.660 --> 00:36:49.180
But by the year 2100,
in 100 years' time,

00:36:49.180 --> 00:36:52.320
we will become Type 1.

00:36:52.320 --> 00:36:55.350
And that gives us
room for hope that we

00:36:55.350 --> 00:36:58.500
will be a planetary
civilization by 2100.

00:36:58.500 --> 00:37:01.350
For example, what
language will they speak?

00:37:01.350 --> 00:37:04.440
Already the two
languages on the internet

00:37:04.440 --> 00:37:08.760
are English and
Mandarin Chinese.

00:37:08.760 --> 00:37:10.900
Look at the internet.

00:37:10.900 --> 00:37:12.340
What is the internet?

00:37:12.340 --> 00:37:15.750
The internet is the
first Type 1 technology

00:37:15.750 --> 00:37:18.300
to arrive in this century.

00:37:18.300 --> 00:37:21.360
That's what the internet
is-- the first Type 1

00:37:21.360 --> 00:37:23.710
technology to arrive.

00:37:23.710 --> 00:37:27.300
That we have the European
Union, Type 1 economy.

00:37:27.300 --> 00:37:33.840
We have the beginning of a Type
I sports, Olympics, soccer.

00:37:33.840 --> 00:37:36.340
We have the beginning
of a Type 1 music,

00:37:36.340 --> 00:37:39.990
rock and roll, rap music, yuck.

00:37:39.990 --> 00:37:42.270
We have the beginning
of a Type 1 culture.

00:37:42.270 --> 00:37:45.090
But it's not
guaranteed that we will

00:37:45.090 --> 00:37:47.730
make the transition to Type 1.

00:37:47.730 --> 00:37:51.270
Because we still have all the
savagery, all the backwardness,

00:37:51.270 --> 00:37:53.280
of our ancient past.

00:37:53.280 --> 00:37:57.150
By the way, I once spoke in
London at the planetarium.

00:37:57.150 --> 00:37:59.165
And a little boy comes up to me.

00:37:59.165 --> 00:38:04.050
The little boy says,
Professor, you're wrong.

00:38:04.050 --> 00:38:04.830
You're wrong.

00:38:04.830 --> 00:38:07.200
There's Type 4.

00:38:07.200 --> 00:38:10.340
And so I told him, look, kid.

00:38:10.340 --> 00:38:10.860
Look, kid.

00:38:10.860 --> 00:38:13.530
There are planets,
stars, and galaxies.

00:38:13.530 --> 00:38:15.240
That's it, folks.

00:38:15.240 --> 00:38:17.760
Planets, stars, and galaxies.

00:38:17.760 --> 00:38:20.928
Therefore, we have
Type 1, Type 2, Type 3.

00:38:20.928 --> 00:38:22.470
And he said, Professor,
you're wrong.

00:38:22.470 --> 00:38:24.300
There's Type 4.

00:38:24.300 --> 00:38:27.660
I said what energy
is beyond galactic?

00:38:27.660 --> 00:38:31.060
And he said the continuum.

00:38:31.060 --> 00:38:35.280
Now who here is a Trekkie who
understands what I just said?

00:38:35.280 --> 00:38:37.560
What is the only
Type 4 civilization

00:38:37.560 --> 00:38:40.710
on network television?

00:38:40.710 --> 00:38:44.110
The Q-- if you
did not understand

00:38:44.110 --> 00:38:49.470
what just transpired,
get with the program.

00:38:49.470 --> 00:38:51.460
The Q is extragalactic.

00:38:51.460 --> 00:38:53.260
And what is that energy--

00:38:53.260 --> 00:38:54.980
dark energy.

